{"type":"message","id":"2e6f1d53","parentId":"ed882fc0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T15:25:07.267Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-03-18 23:25 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 创建一个高质量的汇报管理制度PPT，不少于50页。使用python-pptx库生成。\n\n要求：\n1. 使用精美的企业配色方案（深蓝+金色+玫红）\n2. 全文使用微软雅黑字体\n3. 内容详实丰富，涵盖：\n   - 封面、目录\n   - 为什么要做汇报（员工/管理者/公司价值）\n   - 不做汇报的后果\n   - 三大系统架构（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n   - 汇报管理闭环\n   - 日报四大板块详解\n   - 经验沉淀方法\n   - 明日计划SMART\n   - 点评管理规范\n   - 评分标准体系\n   - 外勤管理规范\n   - 晨会与夕会\n   - 核心原则总结\n   - 结束页\n4. 设计美观，使用卡片式布局、扁平化风格\n5. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/汇报管理制度培训.pptx\n\n请先安装python-pptx库，然后创建完整的PPT代码并执行。"}],"timestamp":1773847507264}}
{"type":"message","id":"05313e2a","parentId":"2e6f1d53","timestamp":"2026-03-18T15:25:14.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a high-quality PowerPoint presentation about reporting management system with at least 50 pages. Let me break down the requirements:\n\n1. Use python-pptx library\n2. Enterprise color scheme: deep blue + gold + magenta red\n3. Use Microsoft YaHei font throughout\n4. Content includes:\n   - Cover page, table of contents\n   - Why reporting (value for employees/managers/company)\n   - Consequences of not reporting\n   - Three major system architectures (DJOS/DJMS/DJAS)\n   - Reporting management closed loop\n   - Daily report four major sections\n   - Experience accumulation methods\n   - Tomorrow's plan SMART\n   - Review management standards\n   - Scoring standards system\n   - Field work management standards\n   - Morning and evening meetings\n   - Core principles summary\n   - End page\n5. Beautiful design with card layout, flat style\n6. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/汇报管理制度培训.pptx\n\nFirst, I need to install python-pptx, then create the code and execute it.","thinkingSignature":"6cf982267d5e93808d2c4ecbcaab7b228b709d3d193350e2e4166104543b6800"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gefjg7vk23cj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pip install python-pptx -q","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":44,"output":273,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":28941,"totalTokens":29258,"cost":{"input":0.000013199999999999999,"output":0.0003276,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0034729199999999996,"total":0.0038137199999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773847507266}}
